The '''Royal British Colonial Society of Artists''' ('''RBC''')<ref name="wordsworth">{{cite book|last1=Dale|first1=Rodney|title=The Wordsworth Dictionary of Abbreviations and Acronyms|date=1997|publisher=Wordsworth|isbn=9781853263859|page=136|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=JxSVKd7D7i4C&lpg=PA136&ots=XhOYxHMD0E&dq=RBC%20royal%20british%20colonial&pg=PA136#v=onepage&q=RBC%20royal%20british%20colonial&f=false}}</ref> was founded in 1887 as the '''Royal Anglo Australian Society of Artists'''<ref name="art-biog">{{cite web|title=Royal British Colonial Society of Artists|url=http://www.artbiogs.co.uk/2/societies/royal-british-colonial-society-artists|publisher=Artist Biographies|accessdate=5 June 2016}}</ref> and received its [[royal charter]] under its later name in 1907.<ref name="times-1909-09-27">{{cite news|title=News in Brief: Royal British Colonial Society of Artists|url=http://find.galegroup.com/ttda/newspaperRetrieve.do?sgHitCountType=None&sort=DateDescend&tabID=T003&prodId=TTDA&resultListType=RESULT_LIST&searchId=R1&searchType=BasicSearchForm&currentPosition=57&qrySerId=Locale%28en%2C%2C%29%3AFQE%3D%28tx%2CNone%2C41%29royal+british+colonial+society+of+artists%24&retrieveFormat=MULTIPAGE_DOCUMENT&userGroupName=lancs&inPS=true&contentSet=LTO&&docId=&docLevel=FASCIMILE&workId=&relevancePageBatch=CS169015611&contentSet=UDVIN&callistoContentSet=UDVIN&docPage=article&hilite=y|accessdate=5 June 2016|work=The Times|date=27 September 1909|page=10|quote=The King has been graciously pleased to grant a charter and diploma to ... The Society, which has now been in existence 21 years ...|subscription=yes}}</ref>
Its members were artists from Britain (notably members of the [[Newlyn School]]), South Africa, Canada, India, New Zealand and Australia.<ref name=art-biog />
It is known to have held an exhibition at the [[Royal Institute Galleries]] in London in 1937<ref name="times-1937-05-08">{{cite news|title=Art Within the Empire: Characteristic examples|url=http://find.galegroup.com/ttda/newspaperRetrieve.do?sgHitCountType=None&sort=DateDescend&tabID=T003&prodId=TTDA&resultListType=RESULT_LIST&searchId=R1&searchType=BasicSearchForm&currentPosition=10&qrySerId=Locale%28en%2C%2C%29%3AFQE%3D%28tx%2CNone%2C41%29royal+british+colonial+society+of+artists%24&retrieveFormat=MULTIPAGE_DOCUMENT&userGroupName=lancs&inPS=true&contentSet=LTO&&docId=&docLevel=FASCIMILE&workId=&relevancePageBatch=CS202715304&contentSet=UDVIN&callistoContentSet=UDVIN&docPage=article&hilite=y|accessdate=5 June 2016|work=The Times|date=8 May 1937|subscription=yes}}</ref> and this is believed to have been its last.<ref name=art-biog />
