*{{cite news|ref={{SfnRef|Pareles|1992}}|last1=Pareles|first1=Jon|title=La Lupe, a Singer, Is Dead at 53; Known as 'Queen of Latin Soul'|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1992/03/07/arts/la-lupe-a-singer-is-dead-at-53-known-as-queen-of-latin-soul.html|accessdate=16 June 2017|work=The New York Times|date=March 7, 1992}}
